node.text:
🚨 GIVEAWAY only runs in this account, no where else! You’ll only get a DM from this account or from XPPEN🚨

I am finally happy to announce that @xppen and I did another collaboration! 

I reviewed their Artist Pro 16 tablet on my YouTube channel. The link is in my bio if you are interested! 

I am impressed with the performance. Their addition of the X3 chip makes the stylus feel realistic and stable to work with. 

We are also doing a giveaway for our supporters✨
RULES: 
☀️ must follow @xppen and @jyundee 
☀️Like this post 
☀️comment “done” 
☀️your account must be public and must be an “art account” in which you’re an artist of. 

❗️ENDS Sept 19, 11:59 pm ET ❗️ Names will be entered into a raffle and a winner will be randomly chosen and announce a week from this post!

Thank you to everyone for supporting me, and I wish everyone good luck!

September’s physicals 🌟

Tier 3: Izzy vinyl sticker 
Tier 5: Izzy vinyl sticker, Duncan holographic sticker & A5 signed print 

Within the perk, you’ll also get access to exclusive digital perks (I usually finish all of this at the last week of the month). All my patrons get free shipping, and I also ship internationally as well. Some locations can have trade restrictions which cause delay. These will be available until the end of September. More info at my patreon (link in bio) thank you to my patrons for supporting me! It means so much!

node.text:
Hello! Here is a NEW #DTIYS 😁

RULES:
🌷tag me on your post. 
🌷use #jyundeeart and #drawthisinyourstyle on the post description.
🌷post the 2nd image on the second slide of yours.
🌷you can change the expression and pose, hair, etc. as along as she is still recognizable. 
🌷you can paint digitally and traditionally 

❗️Challenged will end on Sept 24❗️

I will be sharing some of my favorites on my stories and include it into my highlight section of my profile. 

Have fun!! ♥️

#jyundee #digitalpainting #semirealism #characterart #fantasyart #painting #fashion
